'''加拿大政府'''（{{lang-en|'''Government of Canada'''}}；{{Lang-fr|'''Gouvernement du Canada'''}}），正式名稱為'''女王陛下政府'''（{{lang-en|'''Her Majesty's Government'''}}；{{Lang-fr|'''Gouvernement de Sa Majesté'''}}），是管理[[加拿大|加拿大]]的[[联邦政府|联邦政府]]，並透過共同機關對普通貨物徵收稅款<ref name = MacLeod18>{{Citation |last = MacLeod |first = Kevin S. |authorlink = Kevin S. MacLeod |title = A Crown of Maples |place = Ottawa |publisher = Queen's Printer for Canada |page = 18 |year = 2008 |edition = 1 |url = http://www.canadiancrown.com/crown-of-maples-2012.html |isbn = 978-0-662-46012-1 |accessdate = 21 June 2009 |ref = harv |archive-date = 2015-01-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150115112313/http://www.canadiancrown.com/crown-of-maples-2012.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.speech.gc.ca/eng/frequently-asked-questions-faq |last = Government of Canada |title = Speech From the Throne > Frequently Asked Questions |publisher = Queen's Printer for Canada |accessdate = 4 June 2010 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131019051528/http://www.speech.gc.ca/eng/frequently-asked-questions-faq |archivedate = 2013年10月19日 }}</ref><ref>{{citation |url = http://www.gct3.net/grand-chiefs-office/gct3-info-and-history/government-of-canada-document/ |last = Grand Chief's Office |title = Treaty 3 Between Her Majesty the Queen and the Saulteaux Tribe of the Ojibway Indians at the Northwest Angle on the Lake of the Woods With Adhesions |publisher = The Grand Council of Treaty #3 |accessdate = 4 June 2010 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100404065405/http://www.gct3.net/grand-chiefs-office/gct3-info-and-history/government-of-canada-document/ |archivedate = 2010年4月4日 }}</ref>。在[[加拿大英語|加拿大英語]]中，「Government of Canada」這個詞可能意味著集體機構，或者專指[[行政長官會同行政會議|行政長官會同行政會議]]。這兩種機構在通過《[[1867年英屬北美法令|1867年英屬北美法令]]》且[[加拿大聯邦化|加拿大聯邦化]]後正式成立，其中採行[[聯邦制|聯邦制]]和[[君主立憲制|君主立憲制]]。由[[加拿大君主|加拿大君主]]作為政治基礎核心<ref>{{Citation |last = Department of Canadian Heritage |author-link = Department of Canadian Heritage |title = Canadian Heritage Portfolio |place = Ottawa |publisher = Queen's Printer for Canada |date = February 2009 |edition = 2 |url = http://www.pch.gc.ca/pc-ch/publctn/gp-pg/ppc-chp/ppc-chp-eng.pdf |page = 3 |ISBN = 978-1-100-11529-0 |accessdate = 5 July 2009 |ref = harv |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611162155/http://www.pch.gc.ca/pc-ch/publctn/gp-pg/ppc-chp/ppc-chp-eng.pdf |archivedate = 2011年6月11日 }}</ref>，並且引進[[西敏制|西敏式]]的[[議會制|議會]][[民主|民主]]制度<ref>{{cite journal |last = Coyne |first = Andrew |authorlink = Andrew Coyne |title = Defending the royals |journal = Maclean's |publisher = Rogers Communications |location = Toronto |date = 13 November 2009 |url = http://www2.macleans.ca/2009/11/13/defending-the-royals/ |ISSN = 0024-9262 |accessdate = 17 November 2009 |author =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100227144252/http://www2.macleans.ca/2009/11/13/defending-the-royals/ |archive-date = 2010-02-27 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。加拿大政府治理的相關內容大致在[[加拿大憲法|加拿大憲法]]提及，其他還有幾個世紀來的成文法令、法院裁決以及不成文[[風俗|慣例]]等。當前加拿大政府架構，分成採取[[加拿大樞密院|加拿大樞密院]]轄下的[[加拿大內閣|加拿大內閣]]作為[[行政機構|行政機構]]、[[加拿大國會|加拿大國會]]作為[[立法機構|立法機構]]和各個{{Link-en|加拿大法院系統|Court system of Canada|聯邦法院}}作為[[司法機構|司法機構]]<ref>{{Citation |last = Victoria |author-link = Queen Victoria |publication-date = 29 March 1867 |title = Constitution Act, 1867 |series = III.15 |publication-place = Westminster |publisher = Queen's Printer |url = http://www.solon.org/Constitutions/Canada/English/ca_1867.html |accessdate = 15 January 2009 |year = 1867 |ref = harv |archive-date = 2010-02-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100203024121/http://www.solon.org/Constitutions/Canada/English/ca_1867.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = MacLeod17>{{Harvnb |MacLeod |2008 |p = 17}}</ref><ref>{{Harvnb |Department of Canadian Heritage |2009 |p = 4}}</ref>。

